{"title": "Chvála trnům", "content": "<div style=\"text-align:center\"><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Mikrob je malinký, až není</em></span><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>co by z něj bylo k uvidění,</em></span><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>leč moudří lidé, s mikroskopy</em></span><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>doufají vidět jeho stopy.</em></span><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Členitý jazýček, co stěží</em></span><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>za řadami sta zubů leží;</em></span><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>ocásků sedm chomáčitých,</em></span><br style=\"color:rgba(0,0,0,0.87);background-color:#fafafa\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>růžo-fialo-flíčkovitých.</em></span></div>", "published": "2018-03-22T21:21:00Z", "tags": [], "filename": "/2018/03/chvala-trnum.html"}